title: Sky Eats Airplane - Sky Eats Airplane [2008]
description:
An Electrocore/Screamo outfit from Fort Worth, TX, this band has already released the album, "Everything Perfect on the Wrong Day." This is their second album, self titled, and the first recorded with a full band. Released 7/21/08.

06... Photographic Memory
07... In Retrospect
08... The Artificial
09... Disconnected
10... Machines
11... Alias
